{"type": "article", "id": 14902, "title": "多功能滑板", "description": "", "date": "2015-09-15T07:10:11Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 8, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606060003143rzUZNA01alpWTbt.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\tseasons 推出了三款多功能的手工滑板，它们都能在平路上、水面上和雪地上滑行。滑板主体采用枫木，辅以纤维材料和树脂材料，经过反复实验以保证适应各种环境。三款分别是 alpine（阿尔卑斯）、explorer（探索者）和 antelope（羚羊），它们在长度和性能上有所区别，售价分别是 235 美元、195 美元和 120 美元，<a href=\"http://www.seasonsboards.com/store-road-snow/\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142312ey8NCZiJpWSTFtKa.jpg\" width=\"604\" height=\"308\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.50993377\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142314JF8fIdX3zh20EOaU.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"546\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142314pHAbroUicdkZLnVs.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"382\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.46699267\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}